Package main

Class ProviderDirectoryData

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.ProviderDirectoryData
  • public class ProviderDirectoryData
extends java.lang.Object
    This program creates provider directory data for the provider to see. Once called, it will create a text file and save it onto the terminal for it to be sent as email.
